sequenceDiagram
  participant P as Planner/Caller
  participant O as BackgroundManager
  participant T as TmuxSessionManager
  participant W as Subagent Session
  participant N as Parent Notification

  P->>O: launch(task)
  O->>O: queue + concurrency acquire
  O->>W: create session + promptAsync
  O->>T: onSubagentSessionCreated (optional)
  T->>T: query/decide/execute pane actions
  O->>O: pollRunningTasks + stability checks
  O->>W: session.status/messages
  W-->>O: tool/result output
  O->>N: notifyParentSession
  N-->>P: completion reminder + task output entry
